---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import { business } from "../data/business";
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy | KOM USA" description="How KOM USA handles information submitted through kom-usa.com.">
  <section class="section-pad bg-white"><div class="prose mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 sm:px-6"><h1 class="text-kom-ink text-4xl font-black">Privacy Policy</h1><p class="mt-5 leading-relaxed text-kom-charcoal/75">KOM USA uses information submitted through this website to review and respond to service, estimate, and contact requests.</p><h2 class="text-kom-ink mt-9 text-2xl font-black">Information collected</h2><p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed text-kom-charcoal/75">A request may include your name, phone number, optional email, city or ZIP, optional address, service selection, timing, preferred contact method, project description, source page, and campaign parameters.</p><h2 class="text-kom-ink mt-9 text-2xl font-black">How information is used</h2><p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed text-kom-charcoal/75">Information is used to route the request, contact you about the requested work, review scope, and improve website conversion reporting. Sensitive project descriptions are not intentionally sent to analytics tools. This service-request form does not subscribe you to marketing messages.</p><h2 class="text-kom-ink mt-9 text-2xl font-black">Service providers</h2><p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed text-kom-charcoal/75">The website may use hosting, form-processing, email, analytics, and content-management providers to operate the site and respond to requests.</p><h2 class="text-kom-ink mt-9 text-2xl font-black">Contact</h2><p class="mt-3 leading-relaxed text-kom-charcoal/75">Questions about this policy can be sent to <a class="text-kom-field font-bold" href={business.emailHref}>{business.email}</a>.</p></div></section>
</BaseLayout>
